title: LUNC Cats Wif Hats Collection 1
description:
Welcome to the LUNC Cats Wif Hats Collection! These Cats are looking for a New home from Various Places and Ecosystems and come Bearing gifts in the Form of Staking Rewards By Staking on PixelPact.io!

The Different Rarities for traits will allow different amounts of rewards form the NFT staking pool. Common being the Lowest, and Legendary being the Most. Epic and Legendary NFT Holders will be Eligible for Future Cat Ecosystem Tokens when They Release! But there are also Limited Edition NFT's that will be 1/1 and thy will earn other incentives seperate from The Common - Legendary NFT's.
